		<p class="text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4">Transparent prices with no surprises. Prices include:</p>
		<div class="mb-12 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-2  text-left">
